.IX Subsection "Other API changes"
.PP
\&\f(CW\*(C`guestfs_disk_create\*(C'\fR can now use \s-1VMDK\s0 files as backing files.
.PP
\&\f(CW\*(C`guestfs_btrfs_subvolume_snapshot\*(C'\fR takes extra optional parameters (all
added by Hu Tao):
.ie n .IP """ro""" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWro\fR" 4
