\fIArchitectures\fR
.IX Subsection "Architectures"
.PP
ARMv7 (32 bit) now supports \s-1KVM\s0 acceleration.
.PP
Aarch64 (\s-1ARM 64\s0 bit) is supported, but the appliance part does not work yet.
